    </div><img src="/images/home.avif" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/home-p-500.avif 500w, /images/home-p-800.avif 800w, /images/home-p-1080.avif 1080w, /images/home-p-1600.avif 1600w, /images/home.avif 2194w" alt="Estudio Arquó — imagen de portada del proyecto" class="hero_project_bg" />
