  <section class="desktop_description">
    <div class="description_text_objetive fade-in">
      <h2 class="description_text_objetive_heading">Arquitectura que trasciende: Un escaparate digital para hogares diseñados en calma</h2>
      <div class="u-hflex-between-top full_width">
        <div class="description_title"><img src="/images/diamond.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="description_title_image" />
          <div class="description_title_name">Objetivos</div>
        </div>
        <div class="description_wrapper">
          <div class="description_paragraph">El reto de este proyecto era trasladar la esencia física y tangible de Estudio Arquó —definida por formas puras, luz serena, materiales nobles y proporciones atemporales— al entorno digital. Buscábamos crear un sitio web que no solo funcionara como un portfolio exquisito, sino como el primer &quot;socio creativo&quot; con el que interactúa el usuario.</div>
          <div class="description_paragraph">Encontrar el equilibrio entre un impacto visual puramente estético y fotográfico, y a la vez diseñar un embudo de conversión optimizado para captar y cualificar clientes de alto valor adquisitivo (proyectos desde 300.000€ hasta más de 10.000.000€) era nuestro principal desafío.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div data-w-id="8efec8fe-c4ac-2809-0cd8-c5d2a4d5fce0" class="description_carousel">
      <div class="description_carousel_upperrow fade-in"><img src="/images/horizontal-1.avif" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/horizontal-1-p-500.avif 500w, /images/horizontal-1-p-800.avif 800w, /images/horizontal-1-p-1080.avif 1080w, /images/horizontal-1-p-1600.avif 1600w, /images/horizontal-1-p-2000.avif 2000w, /images/horizontal-1.avif 2816w" alt="Proyecto de arquitectura de Estudio Arquó" class="upper-row-image is1" /><img src="/images/home.avif" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/home-p-500.avif 500w, /images/home-p-800.avif 800w, /images/home-p-1080.avif 1080w, /images/home.avif 1408w" alt="Estudio Arquó — imagen de portada del proyecto" class="upper-row-image is2" /><img src="/images/visualelectric-1.avif" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/visualelectric-1-p-500.avif 500w, /images/visualelectric-1-p-800.avif 800w, /images/visualelectric-1-p-1080.avif 1080w, /images/visualelectric-1-p-1600.avif 1600w, /images/visualelectric-1-p-2000.avif 2000w, /images/visualelectric-1.avif 2816w" alt="Render de arquitectura de Estudio Arquó" class="upper-row-image is3" /><img src="/images/visualelectric-4.avif" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/visualelectric-4-p-500.avif 500w, /images/visualelectric-4-p-800.avif 800w, /images/visualelectric-4-p-1080.avif 1080w, /images/visualelectric-4-p-1600.avif 1600w, /images/visualelectric-4-p-2000.avif 2000w, /images/visualelectric-4.avif 2816w" alt="Render de arquitectura de Estudio Arquó" class="upper-row-image is4" /><img src="/images/image-30_1.avif" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 569px" srcset="/images/image-30_1image%2030.avif 500w, /images/image-30_1image%2030.avif 800w, /images/image-30_1image%2030.avif 1080w, /images/image-30_1.avif 2560w" alt="Proyecto de arquitectura de Estudio Arquó" class="upper-row-image is5" /></div>
      <div class="description_carousel_bottomrow"><img src="/images/casa-albor-1.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/casa-albor-1-p-500.webp 500w, /images/casa-albor-1-p-800.webp 800w, /images/casa-albor-1-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/casa-albor-1-p-1600.webp 1600w, /images/casa-albor-1-p-2000.webp 2000w, /images/casa-albor-1-p-2600.webp 2600w, /images/casa-albor-1-p-3200.webp 3200w, /images/casa-albor-1.webp 4224w" alt="Casa Albor, proyecto de Estudio Arquó" class="bottom-row-image is1" /><img src="/images/casa-albor-3.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/casa-albor-3-p-500.webp 500w, /images/casa-albor-3-p-800.webp 800w, /images/casa-albor-3-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/casa-albor-3-p-1600.webp 1600w, /images/casa-albor-3-p-2000.webp 2000w, /images/casa-albor-3-p-2600.webp 2600w, /images/casa-albor-3-p-3200.webp 3200w, /images/casa-albor-3.webp 4224w" alt="Casa Albor, proyecto de Estudio Arquó" class="upper-row-image-copy is2" /><img src="/images/casa-albor-7.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/casa-albor-7-p-500.webp 500w, /images/casa-albor-7-p-800.webp 800w, /images/casa-albor-7-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/casa-albor-7-p-1600.webp 1600w, /images/casa-albor-7-p-2000.webp 2000w, /images/casa-albor-7-p-2600.webp 2600w, /images/casa-albor-7-p-3200.webp 3200w, /images/casa-albor-7.webp 4224w" alt="Casa Albor, proyecto de Estudio Arquó" class="bottom-row-image is3" /><img src="/images/casa-albor-10.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/casa-albor-10-p-500.webp 500w, /images/casa-albor-10-p-800.webp 800w, /images/casa-albor-10-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/casa-albor-10-p-1600.webp 1600w, /images/casa-albor-10-p-2000.webp 2000w, /images/casa-albor-10-p-2600.webp 2600w, /images/casa-albor-10-p-3200.webp 3200w, /images/casa-albor-10.webp 4224w" alt="Casa Albor, proyecto de Estudio Arquó" class="bottom-row-image is4" /><img src="/images/la-encina-1.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/la-encina-1-p-500.webp 500w, /images/la-encina-1-p-800.webp 800w, /images/la-encina-1-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/la-encina-1-p-1600.webp 1600w, /images/la-encina-1-p-2000.webp 2000w, /images/la-encina-1-p-2600.webp 2600w, /images/la-encina-1-p-3200.webp 3200w, /images/la-encina-1.webp 4224w" alt="Proyecto La Encina de Estudio Arquó" class="upper-row-image is5" /></div>
